PrecisRe-appointment of MOHAMMED AZHAR ALI KHAN, of Nepean, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Ottawa/Atlantic Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective September 30, 1998.
